&lt;h3&gt;Slow Times at Gold Rush Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I ran across a reference to a post from 2004 explaining &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://www.goldrushgames.com/"&gt;Gold Rush
Games&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20040803005822/http://www.goldrushgames.com/forums/index.php?act=ST&amp;amp;f=2&amp;amp;t=384"&gt;current plans&lt;/a&gt;.
